Name: HULL COLOUR
Explanation: THE COLOUR OF THE HULL OF A PLEASURE CRAFT.

Name: PLUME COLOUR AT LAUNCH
Explanation: THE COLOUR OF A SURFACE-TO-AIR MISSILE'S PLUME AT LAUNCH.

Name: MUZZLE FLASH COLOUR
Explanation: THE COLOR OF ANTI-AIRCRAFT ARTILLERY'S MUZZLE FLASH.

Name: BODY COLOUR
Explanation: THE COLOUR OF THE MAIN SECTION OF A VEHICLE.

Name: MINE ZONE COLOUR CODE
Explanation: THE COLOUR CODE DESIGNATED TO REPRESENT THE STATUS OF MINED CHANNELS.

Name: COLOUR OF EYES
Explanation: THE COLOUR OF THE EYES OF AN INDIVIDUAL.

Name: COLOUR OF HAIR
Explanation: THE PREDOMINANT HAIR COLOUR OF AN INDIVIDUAL.

Name: PLUME COLOUR IN FLIGHT
Explanation: THE COLOUR OF A SURFACE-TO-AIR MISSILE'S PLUME IN FLIGHT.

Name: TRACER COLOUR
Explanation: THE COLOR OF ANTI-AIRCRAFT ARTILLERY TRACERS DURING ENGAGEMENT.

Name: AIRBURST COLOUR
Explanation: THE COLOR OF ORDNANCE AIRBURST AT DETONATION.
